Pursue Lilith and Vhenard through the mines
Pursue Lilith and Vhenard
Neyrelle, Vigo, and I must pursue Lilith and Vhenard, Neyrelle's mother. Their trail leads us to the Condemned Mines.
With my new allies, Neyrelle and Vigo, I must venture into the Condemned Mines to pursue Lilith and Vhenard, Neyrelle's mother.

With my new allies, Neyrelle and Vigo, I must venture into the Condemned Mines to pursue Lilith and Vhenard, Neyrelle's mother.
Pursue Lilith and Vhenard
Inspect the door

Neyrelle has squeezed through a gap in the rocks to find a way to unlock a door from the other side leaving myself and Vigo to fight for our lives. Beyond the door we can continue our pursuit of Lilith and Vhenard, Neyrelle's mother.
Pursue Lilith and Vhenard
Slay the approaching monsters
With my allies in tow, we must fight our way deeper into the mines. Down here the tunnels seem less stable, but we cannot turn back now. We must pursue Lilith and Vhenard, Neyrelle's mother.
Pursue Lilith and Vhenard with Vigo and Neyrelle
Pursue Lilith and Vhenard with Vigo and Neyrelle

Neyrelle, Vigo, and I venture further into the Condemned Mines in pursuit of Lilith and Vhenard, Neyrelle's mother, enduring falling rocks and countless unspeakable creatures. We must find a way through.
Escape the mines
Use the opening to escape the mines
